01:00:57,520 --> 01:00:58,661
[SPEAKER_02]: said the wrong word.

599
01:00:58,801 --> 01:01:08,886
[SPEAKER_02]: And I just, we have to find a way past those hiccups because I think they are catastrophic in terms of the relationship that we're trying to have with parents.

